OL,3,CFormer MP reprimanded for 'brazen'
OL,4,Csexual misconduct
OL,6,FWords by Political Reporter Lewis
OL,7,FWarner
OL,9,FFormer Conservative MP Aaron Bell has
OL,10,Fbeen reprimanded by the parliamentary
OL,11,Fwatchdog after an investigation found
OL,12,Fhe committed "brazen and drunken"
OL,13,Fsexual misconduct.
OL,15,FThe report from Parliament's Standards
OL,16,FCommissioner revealed that Mr Bell,
OL,17,Fwho represented Newcastle-under-Lyme,
OL,18,Finappropriately touched a female staff
OL,19,Fmember without her consent while
OL,20,Fdrinking in the House of Commons'
OL,21,FStranger's Bar in December 2023.
