OL,6,FHe added: "I have let down the loyal
OL,7,Fmembers of my association and thank
OL,8,Fthem for the support they gave me as a
OL,9,FMember of Parliament.
OL,11,F"I would also like to apologise to the
OL,12,Fpeople of Newcastle-under-Lyme, whom
OL,13,Fit was an honour to serve".
OL,15,FAn independent panel assessing the
OL,16,Fcase noted that Mr Bell's actions
OL,17,Frepresented a serious abuse of power
OL,18,Fand carried a lasting effect on the
OL,19,Fcomplainant.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
