OL,6,FAs he is no longer an MP the range of
OL,7,Fsanctions that could be applied is
OL,8,Flimited.
OL,10,FThe panel stated that it would have
OL,11,Frecommended a lengthy suspension from
OL,12,FParliament had Mr Bell still been
OL,13,Fserving.
OL,15,FThe Independent Expert Panel (IEP),
OL,16,Fchaired by retired judge Rt. Hon Sir
OL,17,FStephen Irwin, handles misconduct
OL,18,Fcases involving MPs, and noted that
OL,19,Fthe setting of a bar did not reduce
OL,20,Fthe severity of Mr Bell's actions.
