OL,6,FMr Bell told the investigation that
OL,7,Fhe'd been "clearly drunk", after he'd
OL,8,Fpreviously been at other drinks
OL,9,Freceptions before going to the bar,
OL,10,Fwhere he joined the complainant and
OL,11,Ftwo witnesses.
OL,13,FAccording to the panel's report, he
OL,14,Fproceeded to touch her thigh, waist
OL,15,Fand bottom, causing her "shock,
OL,16,Fhumiliation and fear".
