OL,6,FAs well as noting that Mr Bell would
OL,7,Fhave faced a significant suspension
OL,8,Fhad he still been an MP, the panel
OL,9,Fsaid it would have also recommended
OL,10,Findefinitely suspending his
OL,11,Fparliamentary pass had he been
OL,12,Feligible for one as a former MP, but
OL,13,Fhe had not served a long enough term
OL,14,Fto be entitled to one.
OL,16,FIt concluded that "the contents of
OL,17,Fthis report will stand as a published
OL,18,Freprimand for the respondent's
OL,19,Fmisconduct".
OL,21,FIn a statement Mr Bell told ITV News:
