OL,9,FCommissioner...
OL,11,F"This investigation was one of the
OL,12,Freasons I chose not to seek re-
OL,13,Felection at the General Election...
OL,15,F"This has been a difficult time for my
OL,16,Ffamily, and I would ask that their
